  <%=safe_join(@kpt.problem_content.split("\n"),tag(:br))%>
</p>

<p>
  <strong>Problemの達成度:</strong>
  <%= @kpt.problem_status %>
</p>

<p>
  <strong>Try :</strong>
</p>
